methods.name: voteInternal

args.name: voterAccount
args.desc: Account of the voter. Must be the same as Txn.sender for now

args.name: vote
args.desc: Voting record for this vote, including yes, no, abstain, and boycott votes. The contract will verify that the total votes matches the voting power of the account.

methods.desc: Cast internal vote for proposal. This will update the proposal metadata and voting records, but will NOT submit votes to the xGov proposal contract.

methods.name: voteExternal

args.name: extAccounts
args.desc: external accounts to submit votes for. MUST match the ext. accounts pending votes in proposal metadata in the same ORDER.

methods.desc: Submit a vote to the xGov proposal contract for each external account, with approvals and rejections calculated based on the internal vote and absentee mode
